{"tid":133582,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"比女友掉返轉頭食住","createTime":"2017-02-24T17:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T17:22:57.000Z","uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e3b22cc46e910d92ddfe2d12b13811a4573d89d","tid":133582,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"拍拖已經5年以上，本身我佔有慾比較強，一開始食住佢，比左太多壓力佢，後尾我自己有反省，(就)返佢多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最近e一年，唔知係咪見我一直咩都就佢，e家佢話咩就最好做咩，我話唔好佢就發少少脾氣啦，我e家好怕遲d再嚴重d就一發不可收拾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知道佢仲係好鐘意我（小動作細眉細眼野睇得出），其實佢e家係比我迫得多有反彈效果呀，定點，有冇絲打可從女性角度幫我分析下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打同樣情況都可以溝通下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想佢一陣再惡化落去，我fd叫我唔好再打比佢，等佢主動搵我，我要令佢想搵我先有得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bfb6090a645ebe1eb585be437fca789a636dec","tid":133582,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0fd6ebcb9942d3e1e19db05b24fb791a65c67b","tid":133582,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93682f62a3947e673a27a4f0570f6d95e848bec9","tid":133582,"uid":5299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:07:25.000Z","msg":"等佢好似你咁反省"},{"pid":"86c33ddca242a1757227fe2bcdc62702465ff164","tid":133582,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等佢好似你咁反省</blockquote><br />\n暫時唔會囉佢，因佢仲覺得自己冇問題"},{"pid":"e4479c514c622b26b838adbae8407b96d1990cd6","tid":133582,"uid":71742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:09:41.000Z","msg":"咪就係想食住你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46433b7f5377276e0f0ce8f8f51b907dfd80f858","tid":133582,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪就係想食住你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可惜我太善良，我有d後悔我做咩要反省...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a5b124e05b55605b4f03ffa00624b91526c4bb","tid":133582,"uid":56874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe4c01b466a38f38f067711973fb083d00afb42","tid":133582,"uid":73509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:22:57.000Z","msg":"理性同平靜地傾返個問題。<br />\n<br />\n但前提係女朋友夠成熟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}